{"tid":1360410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴登報呢場仗未完!! 大家快D上Twitter!!","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:14:48.000Z","uid":71447,"like":201,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ba1ef7d61a6be145bf6797c6abbe796fb0686f","tid":1360410,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攬炒巴登報呢場仗未完<br />\n 攬炒巴登報呢場仗未完<br />\n 攬炒巴登報呢場仗未完</span><br />\n<br />\n我地要繼續上次G20登報經驗<br />\n今次繼續上Twitter宣傳 將香港變做全球的焦點!!<br />\n<br />\n方法依然好簡單<br />\n1. 上Twitter 用Hashtag #StandwithHK #FightforFreedom<br />\n同時配合番攬炒巴主題 加埋@BorisJohnson開一個Post<br />\n要求Boris Johnson回應我地<br />\n<br />\n2. 然後再入去 #StandwithHK #FightforFreedom 揀幾個Post<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/StandWithHK?src=hash\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FStandWithHK%3Fsrc%3Dhash&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9UYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=76f6d49e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hashtag/StandWithHK?src=hash</a><br />\nReweet一下<br />\nLike一下<br />\nComment一下<br />\n搞掂 得閒的話 做多幾下<br />\n可以做到一個Trend最好<br />\n但最唔到亦都唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請大家謹記 一定一定一定要 脫離同溫層<br />\n連登有用 TG有用 蘋果有用 立場有用 連儂牆有用 和理非有用 勇武有用<br />\n但係國際關注亦都係非常有用!!<br />\n多一個外國人發聲<br />\n就多一分壓力比到中共<br />\n就多一分希望革命成功<br />\n所以請大家千萬千萬唔好放棄國際關注呢個支線任務</strong><br />\n<br />\nTwitter同埋Reddit係兩條非常重要國際戰線<br />\n大家千萬千萬千萬唔好忽略<br />\n希望大家可以養成一個習慣<br />\n用你每日上連登1/100的時間<br />\n盡量利多更多的Twitter<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最後大吉利是講句<br />\n如果解放軍出坦克車 屠城<br />\n你第一時間反應會係嘜?<br />\n調頭走? 做烈士頂坦克車? 衝去外國大使館? 抑或係上連登宣傳? 定係打電話同屋企人講拜拜?<br />\n我的答案會係<br />\n拍片放上Twitter 然後@realDonaldTrump <br />\n然後就係等住帶美軍入城 成功攬炒</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n#FightforFreedom<br />\n#StandwithHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/RhkvtuUcntXSuoVzay/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FRhkvtuUcntXSuoVzay%2Fgiphy.gif&h=254e8117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yert0A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yert0A.png&h=8523d66c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c05f533b1d0d60f432d13234f03abc65961c10e","tid":1360410,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d196668028b48c6e98d65855332a05758e83fbf1","tid":1360410,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd237bf916ef2c954f66f2ac030b7f175e553c6","tid":1360410,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62ff776c21285452070ddabdcc8372f5c7f0507","tid":1360410,"uid":71447,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"請大家謹記<br />\n你而家願意多拎五分鐘出黎係Twitter發聲<br />\n香港革命成功的機會就多0.0000001%<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n聚沙成塔<br />\n聚水成河<br />\n我地總會成功!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n#FightforFreedom<br />\n#StandwithHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EAOkPvEX4AAVK8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEAOkPvEX4AAVK8u.jpg&h=1ecc65c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9c7dac732698020e24f29ccd63658d8deb87509","tid":1360410,"uid":71447,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:50:40.000Z","msg":"大家諗下<br />\n如果全世界更加知道香港而家的狀態<br />\n然後好多國家出旅遊警告<br />\n香港旅遊業受到壓力<br />\n佢地會同政府施壓<br />\n<br />\n你要記住<br />\n政府唔理你<br />\n但政府唔會唔理商界<br />\n<br />\n大家加油推爆佢!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n#FightforFreedom<br />\n#StandwithHK<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EAOVCZ5W4AAtcry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEAOVCZ5W4AAtcry.jpg&h=7638fa59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e370c75b1a3366bedb5ba12b430abed4ea1bda78","tid":1360410,"uid":232229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f22aa53b88b669bf5c9b7023cdb8b27f7e3dd849","tid":1360410,"uid":71447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:54:18.000Z","msg":"大家想遍地開花<br />\n開到十八區<br />\n開到美英日韓歐澳等等地區<br />\n大家花咁大人力物力出去遊行集會<br />\n而家只需要花多你少少時間同埋精力<br />\n就更加可以係英語國家有更多影響力<br />\n希望大家可以一齊去Twitter<br />\n推爆佢<br />\n<br />\n而家出面好多五毛嘗試將個風帶去<br />\n群眾鬥群眾<br />\n希望大家可以心水清 唔好中計<br />\n做番我地主線任務<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n#FightforFreedom<br />\n#StandwithHK"},{"pid":"f12b236fd91cd6d9b1f8eae0ce1aa9a23c0df34e","tid":1360410,"uid":71447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴團隊己經講到明<br />\n今次係《中英聯合聲明》之戰首輪攻勢<br />\n即係嚟緊仲會有其他攻勢<br />\n我地或者無能力去幫手撰文<br />\n但我地有能力去制造一個更大的迴響<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以響應<br />\n一齊上Twitter 推爆佢!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n#FightforFreedom<br />\n#StandwithHK"},{"pid":"50b652cb88e5cc046d5e9fd7baffabb6c4385083","tid":1360410,"uid":71447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"請大家一齊推爆Twitter!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong><br />\n#FightforFreedom<br />\n#StandwithHK"},{"pid":"4a3c97b1daa6922d763ad402af96196b47118e6a","tid":1360410,"uid":71447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好淨係放低一個正評就算數<br />\n請你地多行一步<b